  "texts": [
    "This optimization ensures that the additional complexity introduced by measuring diversity does not significantly impact the overall computational efficiency of the algorithms.",
    "Secondly, the scipy.qmc module's design for flexibility and scalability makes it suitable for a wide range of applications, from simple experimental setups to more complex, high-dimensional optimization problems.",
    "This versatility is particularly beneficial in academic research, where the diversity of inquiry often necessitates adaptable computational tools.",
    "The choice to leverage the Scipy library is further justified by the precision and reliability it brings to the computational experiments.",
